# Environment Variables Template

A comprehensive template for configuring environment variables in Claude code projects. Copy the relevant sections to your `.env` file and populate with your values.

---

## Application Core

```bash
# ============================================
# APPLICATION SETTINGS
# ============================================

# Application Environment
NODE_ENV=                    # development | staging | production
APP_ENV=                     # local | dev | staging | prod
DEBUG=                       # true | false

# Application Identity
APP_NAME=
APP_VERSION=
APP_URL=
APP_PORT=
APP_HOST=

# Locale & Timezone
TZ=                          # e.g., UTC, America/New_York
DEFAULT_LOCALE=              # e.g., en-US
```

